-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-20\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-12-22\" who=\"#JP\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2021-02-22\" who=\"#VM\">Valentina Mignosa encoded text division, cleaned up the autogenerated text and checked the edition\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2025-12-18\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag revised metadata and added image\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2026-01-19\" who=\"#DD\">Dmitry Dundua's lemmatizations were added from source CoNLL-U files\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2026-01-19\" who=\"#RC\">Robert Crellin integrated lemmatizations into EpiDoc using PyEpiDoc and associated scripts\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2026-02-02\" who=\"#RG\">tagged names and persons\u003C/change>\n            \u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic001479_tiled.tif\" height=\"1961px\" width=\"4368px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2015-01-13\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic001479.jpg\" height=\"1961px\" width=\"4368px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2015-01-13\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n        \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#VM\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>\u003Cw n=\"5\">Κλεινοῦς\u003C/w>\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"simple-lemmatized\" resp=\"#DD #RC\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Cw n=\"5\" lemma=\"Κλεινώ\">Κλεινοῦς\u003C/w>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>Text of Dubois, checked against photograph\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>Of Kleinoi\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>The nominative feminine form would be Κλεινώι. The exact form of the monument is not clear, perhaps made up of several elements of which this would be the uppermost. There is no full formal edition of this piece with proper study of its material form, dimensions, etc.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>34.0939\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscript